item.title: CVE-2017-0910|2024-09-17T01:26:15.105Z -- zulip -- zulip%20server
item.description: In Zulip Server before 1.7.1, on a server with multiple realms, a vulnerability in the invitation system lets an authorized user of one realm on the server create a user account on any other realm.
